    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论您的背景与兴趣为何，《坦克世界》都能满足您的渴望：尽情试试不同战术、战车与模式！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗与战术</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《坦克世界》有着独一无二的游戏节奏。游戏中的装甲战车能快能慢，在您快速进入对战同时，也能把握充足时间来思考战略。具有灵敏的反射神经肯定能带来优势，然而真正决定胜败的，则是聪明且大胆的战术运用。找出敌方团队防线上的破口，在正确时间点移动到优势位置，或突袭对手，掌握克敌精要，您就能无往不利且连战皆捷。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/00952f30cf45e9d171c60beec35752ca.poster.avif?t=1771524986\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/00952f30cf45e9d171c60beec35752ca.webm?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/00952f30cf45e9d171c60beec35752ca.mp4?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法多元</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特节奏全操之您手：共有5种战车类型，每种均有截然不同的玩法。一般来说，轻型坦克仰赖速度与隐蔽性，重型坦克以装甲为优势，中型坦克则较为均衡。另外坦克歼击车为令人畏惧的伤害制造机，自行火炮擅长从极远距离炮击对手，甚至能运用即时战略游戏（RTS）般的视角。游戏中有着超过800辆具高度细节的战车，分属于11个等级且来自11个国家，特殊之处不言而喻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/fc9981b6d3da6aa886cc11c10c43f30c.poster.avif?t=1771524986\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/fc9981b6d3da6aa886cc11c10c43f30c.webm?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/fc9981b6d3da6aa886cc11c10c43f30c.mp4?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战车研发与外观自定义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从经典坦克开始，逐步迈向强大的高等级猛兽。利用乘员特长、装备与战地升级来微调战车的性能，让其更为符合您的独特玩法。披上视觉自定义元素来让您的战车更为与众不同，应用自定义涂料、风格与其他众多外观选项，展现每辆战车的独特风采。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/45076d33695942cb3587fcd196d7b5e1.poster.avif?t=1771524986\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/45076d33695942cb3587fcd196d7b5e1.webm?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/45076d33695942cb3587fcd196d7b5e1.mp4?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现代化的视觉呈现与音效</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打从2010年推出迄今，《坦克世界》历经多次大幅度升级，从而提升游戏画面与物理机制。地图上更有着独特的地标与众多可摧毁物件。当战车进入水中会呈现相应的视觉效果，同时遭敌人炮弹命中或击穿时，车体上也会有显著的弹孔，要是反弹炮弹，也会显示出擦痕。火炮击发与炮弹爆炸的效果更是拟真，不仅声响依火炮口径而异，整体环境音效更是层次丰富，让人更为身历其境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/71d2363ae47dce89bb58d67ab6f5e5ad.poster.avif?t=1771524986\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/71d2363ae47dce89bb58d67ab6f5e5ad.webm?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/71d2363ae47dce89bb58d67ab6f5e5ad.mp4?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >众多模式：PVP与各种类型</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中最基本的模式为15v15的随机战。其他重要的常设模式包括天梯战（7v7且具有额外特殊能力）、前线战（巨大地图上的30v30战斗，带来空袭在内的丰富战术选项）与钢铁猎手（具有模式专属战车且可在战斗中升级战车）。此外还有许多带来独特奖励的主题PvE与PvP活动、军团专属的世界地图与根据地，以及其他众多内容！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/8f78156005b634819355c87f0a6a6b63.poster.avif?t=1771524986\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/8f78156005b634819355c87f0a6a6b63.webm?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407200/extras/8f78156005b634819355c87f0a6a6b63.mp4?t=1771524986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >容易上手，适合新手</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管《坦克世界》难以精通，实则容易学习且从一开始便能享受无尽乐趣。身为新玩家，可在训练营情境熟悉基本操作，在低等级战斗面对较容易对付的敌人，也能完成战车培训班来收获诱人奖励。若有好友为资深玩家，更能通过推荐计划助您快速上手，两人也能在过程中获取丰富奖励。</p>",
